{"tid":2310354,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"強制食肆張貼安心出行應對方法","createTime":"2020-12-03T07:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T01:40:50.000Z","uid":216985,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd014b875fc3377318cbdfb1e5e6eee97dbb3b9","tid":2310354,"uid":216985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"極權強制食肆張貼安心出行<br />\n做法同強制張貼政治標語差唔多<br />\n目的係用意識形態管治社會<br />\n我地可能會比極權㩒住黎砌<br />\n我地為左生存<br />\n可能會無辦法唔貼安心出行<br />\n而我地可以做既野係活在真實之中<br />\n盡可能向市民表示掃安心出行係錯誤<br />\n盡可能反抗<br />\n<br />\n作為食肆:<br />\n<br />\n1. 首要行動，拒絕張貼安心出行海報 e.g. 壹碗壹碟<br />\n<br />\n2.如果一定要貼，盡量貼得隱蔽，縮細至睇唔到，標明唔好掃，以不正常方式顯示<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為食客:<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔掃qr code<br />\n<br />\n當然咁樣做係會突出自己<br />\n係要付出代價<br />\n但係為左自己既理念<br />\n呢d代價值唔值得我地去付出呢?<br />\n基於人口稠密 食肆之多<br />\n極權總唔能夠監察每一個角落<br />\n我地總有空間去做一d事<br />\n<br />\n參考:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/suiV2cP2AGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsuiV2cP2AGU&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=ecd416b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/suiV2cP2AGU</a>"},{"pid":"356d595c6ff5302bfd3257023bd747fd9915022f","tid":2310354,"uid":238214,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:46:12.000Z","msg":"貼係地下比食客踏"},{"pid":"df5254813387e7ba25cc3d79c6b678014d83e6bc","tid":2310354,"uid":216985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"356d595c6ff5302bfd3257023bd747fd9915022f","tid":2310354,"uid":238214,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:46:12.000Z","msg":"貼係地下比食客踏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:47:13.000Z","msg":"龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a44dcddb0594662d368be0efa58426cedd489d","tid":2310354,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得反其道而行<br />\n特登印到勁大 e.g. 成個枱面都係<br />\n睇你點scan"},{"pid":"2e87274cf86b83b37c8b995a43adeeac30d54fac","tid":2310354,"uid":216985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"打漏左食客可以做既野<br />\n其實食客可以做更多<br />\n<br />\n2. 盡力支持無貼安心出行既食肆<br />\n<br />\n3. 宣揚唔掃安心出行既理念"},{"pid":"15c6ebfdeea7b7c6f1fd69476538b2738b19a520","tid":2310354,"uid":331739,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"根本應該係集體抵制 咁多黃店有乜好驚<br />\n不過香港人最鐘意就係走精面 搞呢搞路總之要安全抗爭  <br />\n整色整水 咩貼地下啊整花個code 以為好醒<br />\n其實只係不斷將底線下調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47a43bdaf39f28cbbdbdbebe46c0b5f4515d57b","tid":2310354,"uid":216985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5a44dcddb0594662d368be0efa58426cedd489d","tid":2310354,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得反其道而行<br />\n特登印到勁大 e.g. 成個枱面都係<br />\n睇你點scan"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"都係不正常顯示既其中一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要表達到安心出行係並唔係「真相」"},{"pid":"8aa40c3231a3f6d3ecaa6d23edf6f9d335b85462","tid":2310354,"uid":216985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15c6ebfdeea7b7c6f1fd69476538b2738b19a520","tid":2310354,"uid":331739,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"根本應該係集體抵制 咁多黃店有乜好驚<br />\n不過香港人最鐘意就係走精面 搞呢搞路總之要安全抗爭  <br />\n整色整水 咩貼地下啊整花個code 以為好醒<br />\n其實只係不斷將底線下調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:01:37.000Z","msg":"最首要任務一定係幫襯無貼既食肆先<br />\n但係如果真係少食肆唔貼<br />\n唯有做到兩樣野<br />\n<br />\n1. 幫襯肯用剩餘空間反抗既食肆<br />\n<br />\n2. 自己煮"},{"pid":"2f7d2fb29c93cf948b6d3f1c6548e635855d60bc","tid":2310354,"uid":75372,"like":0,"disli